# What NOT to upload when deploying via `gcloud run deploy --source .`
# (Cloud Build uses this; mirrors .dockerignore plus build-context concerns.)
.git
.gitignore
node_modules
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.log
dev-server.log
dev-server.log.err
dev.log
dev.log.err
.DS_Store
README.md
API_SPEC.md
DEPLOY_BACKEND.md
